  "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/abrasive-media-blasting/#content)\n\n# Abrasive Media Blasting\n\n## Sand Blasting\n\n### To SSPC/NACE Standards\n\nOur Abrasive Media Blasting services adhere strictly to the rigorous standards set by SSPC (Society for Protective Coatings) and NACE (National Association of Corrosion Engineers).\n\nUtilizing the necessary equipment and skilled professionals, we ensure that surfaces are meticulously prepared to achieve optimal coating adhesion.\n\nThe process involves removing contaminants and creating a profile suitable for the application of protective coatings, ensuring longevity and performance in diverse environments.\n\n## Our\n\n### Services\n\n- [Wet Paint Coatings](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/wet-paint-coatings/)\n- [Complex Coating](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/complex-coating/)\n- [Abrasive Media Blasting](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/abrasive-media-blasting/)\n- [Powder Coating](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/powder-coating/)\n- [Large Capacity Powder Coating](https://popsindustrial.com/industrial-coatings-services/large-capacity-powder-coating/)\n\n[Get a Quote](https://popsindustrial.com/request-a-quote/)",
